history.content:
The Data Science Department under the ASUC Office of Senator Chen is developing a mentorship program for Data Science students. This program is a semester-long opportunity for current students in data science to guide students who are looking for help with recruitment, career options, or general guidance.

The program will be flexible to your own schedules, and you can make it as interactive as you would like. If you are looking for ways to give back to the Data Science community at Berkeley, or want a network for data science-related professional development, apply to be part of the program!
-----------
Application: tinyurl.com/dsmentorship
Due: Saturday, October 10
